{"tid":1090220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學課舔走濺下顎化學品　中二生灼傷舌頭","createTime":"2019-04-03T10:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T12:22:58.000Z","uid":62063,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e553bb5c9620a10897f4e1870549d90e1ff1a547","tid":1090220,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山東華三院黃鳳翎中學有學生遭化學品灼傷。下午2時48分，一名中二男生於科學課期間，遭化學品灼傷臉部。救護人員接報到場，將傷者送往威爾斯親王醫院治理，其傷勢輕微無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，事發時老師將一瓶化學品傳給學生，傳至事主時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其下顎被化學品濺中感到灼熱，其後事主再伸出舌頭舔走下顎的化學品，灼傷舌頭</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n東華三院黃鳳翎中學校長李靖邦回覆查詢時表示，涉事化學品為氫氯酸，校方已將事件報告予辦學團體，其餘事情不便透露。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ba15da8d099abea7ce6b01f9a990b7c40fc06a","tid":1090220,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"東華三院啲人..."},{"pid":"11a8a4a8031e1dfe132e0646cdc715e4e459f39c","tid":1090220,"uid":155095,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-480u37mgay/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/72768/54988/MGNF46_9__96462.1475007613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn11.bigcommerce.com%2Fs-480u37mgay%2Fimages%2Fstencil%2F1280x1280%2Fproducts%2F72768%2F54988%2FMGNF46_9__96462.1475007613.jpg&h=3f3939c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cb0547dd9c7d7ae19ba97e4bfb17c499281220e","tid":1090220,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"茄汁咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6dd91933375aee28ab9345f3dc1789b5d919fb","tid":1090220,"uid":131884,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"知點解依家細路D遊樂場咁安全<br />\n<br />\n原來真係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\